videos.description: Dejan Vasiljevic hits a 3-pointer in the right corner pocket for the Hurricanes.
videos.headline: Miami's Vasiljevic swishes a corner 3-pointer

videos.description: Chris Lykes finds Lonnie Walker IV for an alley-oop dunk for the Hurricanes.
videos.headline: Miami's Lykes tees up Walker IV for a two-handed dunk

videos.description: Lonnie Walker IV gets the rebound, races the length of the floor and scores a right-handed layup for the Hurricanes.
videos.headline: Walker IV goes coast-to-coast and scores an off-glass layup

videos.description: Jose Alvarado cuts to the lane, gets the handoff and makes a one-handed layup off glass for the Yellow Jackets.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Alvarado scores layup off glass

videos.description: Ben Lammers hits a 17-foot jumper to extend the lead for the Yellow Jackets.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech Lammers hits rhythm jumper

videos.description: Brandon Alston hits a layup off the block shot of Miami's Bruce Brown. Jr for the Yellow Jackets.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Alston scores hustle layup

videos.description: Josh Okogie hits a deep 3-pointer from the top of the key for the Yellow Jackets.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Okogie sings the nylon song with a deep 3

videos.description: Anthony Lawrence II gets the ball, paces up the floor and scores an easy layup for the Hurricanes.
videos.headline: Miami's Lawrence sinks right-handed layup

videos.description: Josh Okogie catches the deflected pass, and scores an off glass layup for the Yellow Jackets.
videos.headline: Okogie scores layup basket off crazy play

videos.description: Josh Okogie gets the handoff, drive the lane and slams home the basket to continue career night
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Okogie continues career night with slam dunk
